[[NHK]]'s 1991 [[taiga drama]] ''[[Taiheiki (TV series)|Taiheiki]]'' was noted for its portrayal of [[Ashikaga Takauji]] as an agent of change against the decadent Hōjō, rather than a national traitor as generally viewed by Japanese historians.
